data.title: Southeastern Technical College
data.meta_description: Southeastern Technical College offers numerous institutional scholarships for students. Awards may be merit-based, academic or athletic.
data.text:
Southeastern Technical College is a unit of the Technical College System of Georgia. Southeastern Tech's main campus is located in Vidalia, with satellite campuses in Glennville and Swainsboro, and distance learning centers in other counties of its service region. The college provides vocational and adult education to students in Candler, Emanuel, Jenkins, Johnson, Montgomery, Tattnall, Toombs, and Treutlen counties.
